  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to evaluate if a GERD treatment programme, in accordance with current regional
      recommendations, in a company health care setting, has an impact on health related quality of
      life (HRQoL), symptoms, and productivity in GERD patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
