    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female and/or male aged &gt; 18 years

          -  Diagnosis of GERD confirmed

          -  Prescription of GERD treatment or already receiving GERD treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any symptom suggesting a need for further investigation

          -  Previous participation in the present study

          -  Current participation in a clinical study or participation in a clinical study during
             the last 30 days
      </textblock>
